ViewObject.Name: ContractView
ViewObject.SQLQuery: SELECT Contract.ID, Contract.CONTENT_OWNER_ID, Contract.CONTRACT_NUMBER, ContentOwner.NAME Content_owner, ContentOwner.NAME Content_owner_2, ContentOwner.SITE, Contract.FORM, Contract.STATUS, Contract.COMP_SUBS_TO_PROVIDE, Contract.FORMAT_OF_COMP_SUBS, Contract.TYPE, Contract.RELATIONSHIP_OWNER, Contract.RELATIONSHIP_OWNER AS RELATIONSHIP_OWNER_2, Contract.DIVISION, Contract.EFFECTIVE_DATE, Contract.TERM_LENGTH, Contract.CANCELLATION_NOTICE_TERM, Contract.ROLLOVER_DATE, Contract.CANCELLATION_DATE, Contract.CANCELLATION_REASON, Contract.CANCELLATION_EFFECTIVE_DATE, Contract.EXPIRATION_DATE, Contract.AUTO_RENEWS_FLAG, Contract.AUTO_RENEW_TERM_MONTHS, Contract.SIGNATORY, Contract.CONTRACT_SIGNED_DATE, Contract.RIGHTS_TO_BE_RETAINED, Contract.EXCLUSIVITY, Contract.CONTENT_MASTER_OWNER, LTRIM(concat(TechnicalContact.first_name, concat(' ', TechnicalContact.Last_name))) TECHNICAL_Name, LTRIM(concat(TechnicalContact.first_name, concat(' ', TechnicalContact.Last_name))) TECHNICAL_Name_2, Contract.NOTE_FLAG, LTRIM(concat(AgreementContact.first_name,concat(' ', AgreementContact.Last_name))) AGREEMENT_Name, LTRIM(concat(AgreementContact.first_name,concat(' ', AgreementContact.Last_name))) AGREEMENT_Name_2, LTRIM(concat(QAContact.first_name,concat(' ', QAContact.Last_name))) QA_Name, LTRIM(concat(QAContact.first_name,concat(' ', QAContact.Last_name))) QA_Name_2, Contract.AUTO_ADD, Contract.ASSIGNMENT, Contract.ROYALTY_BEARING, NVL((SELECT 'Y' FROM TRAX_CONTRACT_GUARANTEE ContractGuarantee WHERE ContractGuarantee.CONTRACT_ID = Contract.ID AND NVL(ContractGuarantee.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE, SYSDATE - 1) <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) AND NVL(ContractGuarantee.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE, SYSDATE + 1) > TRUNC(SYSDATE) AND ROWNUM = 1), 'N') GUARANTEE, Contract.FAIR_TREATMENT_CLAUSE, Contract.ISSUE_EDITION_COVERAGE, Contract.COMPLETE_CONTENT_SET, Contract.WARRANTY_AND_INDEMNIFICATION, Contract.Governance, Contract.CREATED_BY, Contract.CREATED_DATE, trunc(Contract.CREATED_DATE) as created_by_search, Contract.LAST_UPDATED_BY, Contract.LAST_UPDATED_DATE, trunc(Contract.LAST_UPDATED_DATE) as last_update_date_search, Contract.AGREEMENT_CONTACT_ID, Contract.QA_CONTACT_ID, Contract.TECHNICAL_CONTACT_ID, Contract.NOTE, Contract.ACTIVE_FLAG, ContentOwner.problematic_publisher, Contract.IS_TEMPLATE_FLAG, Contract.TEMPLATE_NAME, Contract.CONTRACT_TEMPLATE_ID, Contract.PUBLISHER_CHANGE_CONTRACT_FLAG FROM TRAX_CONTRACT Contract INNER JOIN TRAX_CONTENT_OWNER ContentOwner ON Contract.CONTENT_OWNER_ID = ContentOwner.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_CONTACT AgreementContact ON Contract.AGREEMENT_CONTACT_ID = AgreementContact.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_CONTACT QAContact ON Contract.QA_CONTACT_ID = QAContact.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_CONTACT TechnicalContact ON Contract.TECHNICAL_CONTACT_ID = TechnicalContact.ID WHERE (NVL(Contract.ACTIVE_FLAG,'Y')='Y' OR :SHOW_ALL='ALL') AND Contract.IS_TEMPLATE_FLAG = 'N'
